<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Classigoo - Security Alert</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .alert {
        background-color: #fff3cd;
        color: #856404;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 5px;
        border-left: 5px solid #ffeeba;
      }
      .ip-address {
        background-color: #e9ecef;
        font-family: monospace;
        padding: 5px 10px;
        border-radius: 3px;
      }
      .action-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <h2>Hi {{name}},</h2>

      <div class='alert'>
        We have detected a new login to your Classigoo account from IP address
        <span class='ip-address'>{{ip}}</span>
      </div>

      <p>If this wasn't you, please take immediate action:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Login to your Classigoo account</li>
        <li>Visit the security center</li>
        <li>Review and manage all logged-in devices</li>
        <li>Change your password if necessary</li>
      </ol>

      <a href='/account/security' class='action-button'>
        Visit Security Center
      </a>

      <p>If you need any assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our
        support department.</p>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>Regards,<br />Team Classigoo</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>